          <text><![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><b>Rural Emergency Acute Care Hospital Act</b> </p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"></p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal">This bill revises provisions related to health care in rural areas, including by&nbsp;allowing certain small rural hospitals and critical access hospitals to be designated as rural emergency hospitals for purposes of receiving special payment under Medicare.</p>]]></text>
